snippet.title: Best VGM 2350 - Persona 5 Royal - Ideal and The Real (Takuto Maruki's Theme)
snippet.description:
See also:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS4
Persona 5 Royal (2019)
Ideal and The Real (Takuto Maruki's Theme)
Shoji Meguro & Lyn
